stories.text: We're a small company and growing rapidly with many remote working. We want to start offering company cards to take advantage of all the travel we're reimbursing our employees for now. I'm interested if anyone has experience setting this up and especially any horror stories of how its gone wrong! Is it best to set it all up yourself or are there single companies that do it all for you?
